items.description: The HWID spoofer anonymizes and modifies hardware identifiers on Windows. It includes spoofing for disks, GUIDs, PC names, MAC IDs, installation IDs, EFI bootloaders, SMBIOS data, and displays, along with cache cleaners for games and various system cleaning tools.
